digraph call {
rankdir=TB

# This is what visualization uses.

MultibodyPlant_contact_results_output_port [style=filled,fillcolor=lightgreen]

MultibodyPlant_contact_results_output_port -> MultibodyPlant_CopyContactResultsOutput
MultibodyPlant_CopyContactResultsOutput -> MultibodyPlant_EvalContactResults
MultibodyPlant_EvalContactResults -> DiscreteUpdateManager_EvalContactResults
DiscreteUpdateManager_EvalContactResults -> DiscreteUpdateManager_CalcContactResults

DiscreteUpdateManager_CalcContactResults -> DiscreteUpdateManager_AppendContactResultsForPointContact
DiscreteUpdateManager_CalcContactResults -> DiscreteUpdateManager_AppendContactResultsForHydroelasticContact

DiscreteUpdateManager_AppendContactResultsForPointContact -> MultibodyPlant_EvalPointPairPenetrations
DiscreteUpdateManager_AppendContactResultsForPointContact -> DiscreteUpdateManager_EvalDiscreteContactPairs
DiscreteUpdateManager_AppendContactResultsForPointContact -> DiscreteUpdateManager_EvalContactSolverResults

DiscreteUpdateManager_AppendContactResultsForHydroelasticContact -> DiscreteUpdateManager_EvalHydroelasticContactInfo
DiscreteUpdateManager_EvalHydroelasticContactInfo -> DiscreteUpdateManager_CalcHydroelasticContactInfo

DiscreteUpdateManager_CalcHydroelasticContactInfo -> DiscreteUpdateManager_EvalContactSurfaces
DiscreteUpdateManager_CalcHydroelasticContactInfo -> DiscreteUpdateManager_EvalDiscreteContactPairs
DiscreteUpdateManager_CalcHydroelasticContactInfo -> DiscreteUpdateManager_EvalContactSolverResults

# This is what the LPF consumes.

MultibodyPlant_generalized_contact_forces_output_port [style=filled,fillcolor=pink]

MultibodyPlant_generalized_contact_forces_output_port -> DiscreteUpdateManager_EvalContactSolverResults
DiscreteUpdateManager_EvalContactSolverResults -> DiscreteUpdateManager_CalcContactSolverResults

# This is the timestep solve.

MultibodyPlant_CalcDiscreteStep [style=filled,fillcolor=lightgreen]

MultibodyPlant_CalcDiscreteStep -> DiscreteUpdateManager_CalcDiscreteValues

DiscreteUpdateManager_CalcDiscreteValues -> DiscreteUpdateManager_SampleDiscreteInputPortForces

DiscreteUpdateManager_CalcDiscreteValues -> DiscreteUpdateManager_DoCalcDiscreteValues
DiscreteUpdateManager_DoCalcDiscreteValues -> DiscreteUpdateManager_EvalContactSolverResults

DiscreteUpdateManager_CalcContactSolverResults -> CompliantContactManager_DoCalcContactSolverResults

CompliantContactManager_DoCalcContactSolverResults -> SapDriver_CalcContactSolverResults

SapDriver_CalcContactSolverResults -> SapDriver_EvalSapSolverResults
SapDriver_CalcContactSolverResults -> DiscreteUpdateManager_EvalDiscreteContactPairs
SapDriver_CalcContactSolverResults -> SapDriver_EvalContactProblemCache

SapDriver_EvalSapSolverResults -> SapDriver_CalcSapSolverResults

SapDriver_CalcSapSolverResults -> SapDriver_EvalContactProblemCache
SapDriver_CalcSapSolverResults -> SapSolver_SolveWithGuess

SapDriver_EvalContactProblemCache -> SapDriver_CalcContactProblemCache

DiscreteUpdateManager_EvalDiscreteContactPairs -> DiscreteUpdateManager_CalcDiscreteContactPairs
DiscreteUpdateManager_CalcDiscreteContactPairs -> DiscreteUpdateManager_AppendDiscreteContactPairsForPointContact
DiscreteUpdateManager_CalcDiscreteContactPairs -> DiscreteUpdateManager_AppendDiscreteContactPairsForHydroelasticContact

DiscreteUpdateManager_AppendDiscreteContactPairsForPointContact -> MultibodyPlant_EvalPointPairPenetrations

DiscreteUpdateManager_AppendDiscreteContactPairsForHydroelasticContact -> DiscreteUpdateManager_EvalContactSurfaces
DiscreteUpdateManager_EvalContactSurfaces -> MultibodyPlant_EvalContactSurfaces

MultibodyPlant_EvalContactSurfaces -> MultibodyPlant_CalcHydroelasticWithFallback
MultibodyPlant_CalcHydroelasticWithFallback -> MultibodyPlant_EvalGeometryQueryInput
MultibodyPlant_CalcHydroelasticWithFallback -> QueryObject_ComputeContactSurfacesWithFallback

QueryObject_ComputeContactSurfacesWithFallback [style=filled,fillcolor=orange]

# Color eval functions that depend only on the current configuration ticket in
# the context (presuming no changes to geometry version nor other Parameters).

DiscreteUpdateManager_EvalContactSurfaces [style=filled,fillcolor=cyan]
MultibodyPlant_EvalContactSurfaces [style=filled,fillcolor=cyan]
MultibodyPlant_EvalGeometryQueryInput [style=filled,fillcolor=cyan]
MultibodyPlant_EvalPointPairPenetrations [style=filled,fillcolor=cyan]

# Color eval functions that depend only on the current kinematics ticket in
# the context (presuming no changes to geometry version nor other Parameters).

DiscreteUpdateManager_EvalContactResults [style=filled,fillcolor=pink]
DiscreteUpdateManager_EvalDiscreteContactPairs [style=filled,fillcolor=pink]
DiscreteUpdateManager_EvalHydroelasticContactInfo [style=filled,fillcolor=pink]

# These depend on the configuration AND sampled input forces.

DiscreteUpdateManager_EvalContactSolverResults [style=filled,fillcolor=lightblue]

# These depend on the configuration and ALL INPUTS.

SapDriver_EvalSapSolverResults [style=filled,fillcolor=lightgreen]
SapDriver_EvalContactProblemCache [style=filled,fillcolor=lightgreen]

}